text: Daniel Byrd (born November 20, 1985) is an American actor. He is known for his roles in A Cinderella Story, the 2006 remake of The Hills Have Eyes, the 2010 movies Easy A and Norman, and the sitcoms Aliens in America and Cougar Town.
